    {"class":"privacy","sentence":"(C) The employer needs such findings in order to comply with its obligations, under 29 CFR parts 1904 through 1928, 30 CFR parts 50 through 90, or under state law having a similar purpose, to record such illness or injury or to carry out responsibilities for workplace medical surveillance; and"},
    {"class":"privacy","sentence":"(C) The right to inspect and copy protected health information as provided by Ã‚Â§164.524;"},
