    {"class":"privacy","sentence":"(i) A covered entity may use or disclose a limited data set under paragraph (e)(1) of this section only for the purposes of research, public health, or health care operations."},
    {"class":"privacy","sentence":"(i) A covered entity may, in accordance with paragraphs (b)(2) or (3) of this section, disclose to a family member, other relative, or a close personal friend of the individual, or any other person identified  by the individual, the protected health information directly relevant to such person's involvement with the individual's care or payment related to the individual's health care."},
