    {"class":"privacy","sentence":"(ii) For the covered entity to apply a change in its more limited uses and disclosures to protected health information created or received prior to issuing a revised notice, in accordance with Ã‚Â§164.530(i)(2)(ii), the notice must include the statements required by paragraph (b)(1)(v)(C) of this section."},
